General.Name: Assetowl Ltd
General.Description: AssetOwl Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as technology and software development company in Australia. It offers Pirsee, an inspection management platform that allows multiple users to work on an inspection at the same time. It also offers PropertyMe and Property Tree, a real estate trust tools which together service of Australia residential real estate agents. The company was formerly known as Regalpoint Resources Ltd and changed its name to AssetOwl Limited. The company is based in Perth, Australia.
